          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The detector system consisting of two start and stop",
                "time-of-flight detectors and an array of silicon",
                "detectors."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SISD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".After passing the TOF-detectors, recoil nuclei",
                "are implanted in an array of detectors assembled on the",
                "basis of separate position-sensitive silicon strips.",
                "Eight of such strips having the sensitive area of",
                " 8*64 mm**2 compose the detector array with the",
                "rectangular surface of 67.5*64 mm**2. The typical",
                "energy resolution is about 45 keV for 5.3 MeV alpha-",
                "particles. position resolution is obtained close to",
                " 0.5 mm in each strip."
              ]
            }
          ],
